      "label": "uniqueProductIdentifier",
      "kind": "Property",
      "preferredName": "unique product identifier",
      "description": "\n   Unique string of characters for the identification of a product, that also enables a web link to the digital product passport.\n   \n   String formatted according to EN 18219:2026.\n\n   SOURCE: EN 18223:2026(en)   \n   ",
